253
00:16:00,193 --> 00:16:02,662
Well, the last time I
saw you, before you left...

254
00:16:06,132 --> 00:16:08,692
I screamed at you because
you missed my birthday party.

255
00:16:10,069 --> 00:16:12,629
And for the longest time,

256
00:16:12,705 --> 00:16:14,901
I thought if I
could just tell you...

257
00:16:15,908 --> 00:16:18,707
I was sorry, that
