386
00:25:18,517 --> 00:25:20,850
It'll take at least two
hours for you to run back

387
00:25:20,919 --> 00:25:23,047
- to the campground.
- I'm faster than I look.

388
00:25:23,122 --> 00:25:26,024
You told me you used to skip phys-ed
class because you hated running.

389
00:25:26,091 --> 00:25:28,583
- I can hate it and still be good at it.
- No.

390
00:25:31,730 --> 00:25:34,723
My pocketknife is
as sharp as a scalpel.

391
00:25:34,800 --> 00:25:36,632
The tent repair kit
